    - x1: position at time t
    - x2: velocity at time t

    Parameters:
    - params: array of 12 trainable coefficients

    Model form:

        y = params[0]                       # constant offset
          + params[1]*x0                    # linear in time (drift or forcing)
          + params[2]*x1                    # linear restoring force (-k*x)
          + params[3]*x2                    # linear damping (-c*v)
          + params[4]*(x1**3)               # cubic nonlinearity in position (Duffing term)
          + params[5]*np.sin(x0)            # sinusoidal forcing term at fundamental frequency
