    - cubic position-velocity coupling (x^2 * v) [new]
    - cubic time term (t^3) [new]

    Mathematical form:
        y = p0 
            + p1 * t 
            + p2 * x 
            + p3 * v 
            + p4 * x^3 
            + p5 * v^2
            + p6 * x^2
            + p7 * x * v
            + p8 * v^3
            + p9  * t * x
