    including physically meaningful linear and nonlinear stiffness and damping terms,
    plus possible time-dependent forcing or parametric excitation.

    Parameters:
    - params: array of 12 parameters
        params[0]: constant offset (force)
        params[1]: linear time coefficient (forcing or parametric)
        params[2]: linear stiffness coefficient k (>0 for restoring force)
        params[3]: linear damping coefficient c (>0 for dissipation)
        params[4]: cubic stiffness coefficient alpha (nonlinear restoring force)
        params[5]: quadratic velocity damping coefficient d (nonlinear damping)
        params[6]: quadratic position term coefficient beta
        params[7]: cross term coefficient gamma between position and velocity
        params[8]: quadratic time effect coefficient (parametric modulation)
