    - Linear terms in time, position, velocity
    - Quadratic and cubic nonlinearities in position and velocity
    - Cross terms between position & velocity and time & position
    - Sinusoidal forcing term

    Parameters:
        x0: time array
        x1: position array at time t
        x2: velocity array at time t
        params: array of parameters with length at least 12

            params[0]: constant offset
