    - params (np.ndarray): Trainable coefficients used by the equation skeleton.
    """
    """Improved version of `equation_v1`.

    This version models the acceleration of a nonlinear harmonic oscillator as a combination of:
    - constant offset
    - linear, quadratic, cubic restoring force terms (position-dependent)
    - linear, quadratic, cubic damping terms (velocity-dependent)
    - interaction terms between position and velocity (linear and quadratic)
