            params[3]: linear damping coefficient c (>0), appears as -c*x2
            params[4]: cubic stiffness coefficient alpha (>0), appears as -alpha*x1^3
            params[5]: quadratic velocity damping coefficient c_quad_vel (>0), appears as -c_quad_vel*x2*|x2|
